LogicalColumn.name: Cash Status

Expr.ExprTextDesc: EVALUATE('CASE WHEN %1 IS NULL THEN NULL WHEN MONTHS_BETWEEN(SYSDATE, %1) <= 18 THEN ''Active'' ELSE ''Lapsed'' END' AS VARCHAR ( 30 ), "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_WC_OWN_PARTY_D"."LAST_CASH_DT")

LogicalColumn.name: CoG Status
LogicalColumn.Description: Status to indicate whether the party is one of various states if they are a CoG donor

LogicalColumn.name: Tenure
LogicalColumn.Description: Number of years since first donation date

LogicalColumn.name: Total Donation Count
LogicalColumn.Description: The number of donation records on the Party's record where the donation amount can be positive or negative (includes refunds and reversals).

LogicalColumn.name: Total Donation Amount
LogicalColumn.Description: The total amount given by the Party to the charity (sum of all donations). This is the Gross Amount (inclusive of Gift Aid).

LogicalColumn.name: No of Donations Received
LogicalColumn.Description: The number of donation records on the Party's record where the donation amount is greater than zero.

LogicalColumn.name: Largest Gross Donation Amount
LogicalColumn.Description: Largest Donation Amount including Gift Aid that has been processed (Actual Completed).

LogicalColumn.name: Largest Donation Date
LogicalColumn.Description: The date of the largest donation the owning party has given to CRUK.

LogicalColumn.name: First Gross Donation Amount
LogicalColumn.Description: First Donation Amount including Gift Aid that has been processed (Actual Completed).

LogicalColumn.name: First Donation Date
LogicalColumn.Description: The date of the first donation the owning party has given to CRUK.

LogicalColumn.name: Last Donation Date
LogicalColumn.Description: The date of the last donation the owning party has given to CRUK.

LogicalColumn.name: Total Net Donation Amount
LogicalColumn.Description: The total Net amount given by the Party to the charity (sum of all donations).

LogicalColumn.name: First Net Donation Amount
LogicalColumn.Description: The amount of the first donation the owning party has given to CRUK

LogicalColumn.name: Last Net Donation Amount
LogicalColumn.Description: The amount of the last donation the owning party has given to CRUK

LogicalColumn.name: Largest Net Donation Amount
LogicalColumn.Description: The amount of the largest donation the owning party has given to CRUK

LogicalColumn.name: Last Gross Donation Amount
LogicalColumn.Description: Latest Donation Amount including Gift Aid that has been processed (Actual Completed).

LogicalColumn.name: Stewardship Value
LogicalColumn.Description: This is the Gross Stewardship Value (inclusive of Gift Aid). Stewardship value is the sum of all donations received from the owning party plus any outstanding income still awaited on Proposals of status 'Stewardship'

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: IFNULL("Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_WC_OWN_PARTY_D"."TOTAL_PAY_AMT", 0) + IFNULL("Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_WC_OWN_PARTY_D"."TOTAL_GIFTAID_AMT", 0) - IFNULL("Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_WC_OWN_PARTY_D"."TOTAL_PAY_AMT_SP", 0) - IFNULL("Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_WC_OWN_PARTY_D"."TOTAL_GIFTAID_AMT_SP", 0) + IFNULL("Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_WC_OWN_PARTY_D"."TOTAL_ORDER_GROSS_AMT_SP", 0)

LogicalColumn.name: Stewardship Value Banding
LogicalColumn.Description: This is the banding into which the Gross Stewardship value falls e.g. 10-49k

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Stewardship Value" < 10000 THEN '£0-£9k' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Stewardship Value" < 50000 THEN '£10k-£49k' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Stewardship Value" < 100000 THEN '£50k-£99k' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Stewardship Value" < 500000 THEN '£100k-£499k' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Stewardship Value" < 1000000 THEN '£500k-£999k' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Stewardship Value" >= 1000000 THEN '£1m+' ELSE '' END

LogicalColumn.name: Net Stewardship Value
LogicalColumn.Description: This is the Net Stewardship Value (not including Gift Aid). Stewardship value is the sum of all donations received from the owning party plus any oustanding income still awaited on Proposals of status 'Stewardship'

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: IFNULL("Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_WC_OWN_PARTY_D"."TOTAL_PAY_AMT", 0) - IFNULL("Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_WC_OWN_PARTY_D"."TOTAL_PAY_AMT_SP", 0) + IFNULL("Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_WC_OWN_PARTY_D"."TOTAL_ORDER_GROSS_AMT_SP", 0)

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN IFNULL( LOCATE(' ', "%1"), 0) = 0 THEN "%1" ELSE LEFT("%1", LOCATE(' ', "%1")-1) END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN IFNULL( LOCATE(' ', "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Latest Programme Name"), 0) = 0 THEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Latest Programme Name" ELSE LEFT("Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Latest Programme Name", LOCATE(' ', "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Latest Programme Name")-1) END

LogicalColumn.name: Historic MGA Interest Flag
LogicalColumn.Description: Indicates whether the supporter has at least one CRUK interest record with Department = 'Major Giving & Appeals'

LogicalColumn.name: Current MGA Interest Flag
LogicalColumn.Description: Indicates whether the supporter has at least one CRUK interest record with Department = 'Major Giving & Appeals' without an end date

LogicalColumn.name: MGA Prospect
LogicalColumn.Description: This will be set to 'Y' if the Owning Party is a Prospect and 'N' if they are not. A Prospect is defined as an Owning Party who has a CRUK Interest of Department = 'Major Giving & Appeals' and Type = 'Prospect'.

LogicalColumn.name: MGA Suspect
LogicalColumn.Description: This will be set to 'Y' if the Owning Party is a Suspect and 'N' if they are not. A Suspect is defined as an Owning Party who has a CRUK Interest of Department = 'Major Giving & Appeals' and Type = 'Suspect'.

LogicalColumn.name: Last Thank You Sent Date
LogicalColumn.Description: Shows the date of the most recent activity on the owning party record of Category = MG&A and Sub category = Thank You

LogicalColumn.name: Owning Party ROW_ID
LogicalColumn.Description: Siebel Row Id of the Owning Party (Supporter/Household/Organization)

LogicalColumn.name: Postal Area
LogicalColumn.Description: The first one or two letters of the postcode (anything before the first number). For instance, if the postcode is PL14 4TE, the Postal Area is 'PL'

LogicalColumn.name: Postal District
LogicalColumn.Description: The first section of the postcode, before the last 3 characters. For instance, if the postcode is PL14 4TE, the Postal District is PL14

LogicalColumn.name: Postal Sector
LogicalColumn.Description: The postcode minus the last two letters. For instance, if the postcode is PL14 4TE, the Postal Sector is PL14 4

LogicalColumn.name: VF Region
LogicalColumn.Description: The VF Region which the postal district belongs to as defined in the Postcode Admin table on Siebel e.g. PL14 is in Region 9

LogicalColumn.name: VF Regional Canvasser
LogicalColumn.Description: The Canvasser who is responsible for the area in which the owning party's primary address sits, as defined in the Postcode Admin table on Siebel

LogicalColumn.name: Legacy Region
LogicalColumn.Description: The Legacy Region which the postal district belongs to as defined in the Postcode Admin table on Siebel

LogicalColumn.name: Legacy Regional Canvasser
LogicalColumn.Description: The Regional Legacy Manager who is responsible for the region in which the owning party's primary address sits, as defined in the Postcode Admin table on Siebel

LogicalColumn.name: FWS Scheme Name
LogicalColumn.Description: The name of the Free Will Service scheme that covers the region in which the owning party's primary address sits, as defined in the Postcode Admin table on Siebel

LogicalColumn.name: Supporter Age at Campaign Launch
LogicalColumn.Description: The age of the Supporter at the time the campaign was launched

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_YEAR , "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Supporter Birthday", "Core 2"."Dim - Campaign"."Planned Start Date")

LogicalColumn.name: Supporter Legacy Age Range at Campaign Launch
LogicalColumn.Description: The Legacy Age Range of the Supporter at the time the campaign was launched

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" < 50 THEN 'Under 50' WHEN "%1" >= 50 AND "%1" < 60 THEN '50 - 59' WHEN "%1" >= 60 AND "%1" < 70 THEN '60 - 69' WHEN "%1" >= 70 THEN '70+' WHEN "%1" IS NULL THEN 'Unknown' END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Supporter Age at Campaign Launch" < 50 THEN 'Under 50' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Supporter Age at Campaign Launch" >= 50 AND "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Supporter Age at Campaign Launch" < 60 THEN '50 - 59' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Supporter Age at Campaign Launch" >= 60 AND "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Supporter Age at Campaign Launch" < 70 THEN '60 - 69' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Supporter Age at Campaign Launch" >= 70 THEN '70+' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Supporter Age at Campaign Launch" IS NULL THEN 'Unknown' END

LogicalColumn.name: Fundraising Group Current Level
LogicalColumn.Description: This shows the current, open level for a fundraising group e.g. Nuture, Mid-Income Grow etc

LogicalColumn.name: No of Fundraising Registrations
LogicalColumn.Description: This shows how many fundraising registrations the owning party has had

LogicalColumn.name: Total VF Amount Raised
LogicalColumn.Description: This shows the total amount of income which the owning party has returned to products in the Product group of 'Volunteer Fundraising' or a Product Code of 'REVF', over the lifetime of the Owning Party

LogicalColumn.name: Total Fundraising Registration Income
LogicalColumn.Description: This shows the total Fundraising Registration income returned for this owning party. Fundraising Registration Income is defined as ‘Any income received for this owning party since the fundraising registration date & before their next fundraising registration date up to maximum 24 months, of product code FUNDON or BCADON’

LogicalColumn.name: Primary Phone (UK Only)
LogicalColumn.Description: Primary Phone Number for the Owning Party (only populated if the number is not of type 'Telephone - International')

LogicalColumn.name: Primary Phone (International Only)
LogicalColumn.Description: Primary Phone Number for the Owning Party (only populated if the number is of type 'Telephone - International')

LogicalColumn.name: Primary Mobile (UK Only)
LogicalColumn.Description: Primary Mobile Number for the Owning Party (only populated if the number is not of type 'Mobile - International')

LogicalColumn.name: Primary Mobile (International Only)
LogicalColumn.Description: Primary Mobile Number for the Owning Party (only populated if the number is of type 'Mobile - International')

LogicalColumn.name: Organisation Primary Contact Salutation
LogicalColumn.Description: Organisation Primary Contact Salutation: The salutation of the Supporter who is marked as a Primary Contact for an Organisation.

LogicalColumn.name: Organisation Primary Contact Label Name
LogicalColumn.Description: Organisation Primary Contact Label Name: The label name of the Supporter who is marked as a Primary Contact for an Organisation.

LogicalColumn.name: Organisation Primary Contact Preferred Name
LogicalColumn.Description: Organisation Primary Contact Preferred Name: The preferred name of the Supporter who is marked as a Primary Contact for an Organisation.

LogicalColumn.name: Organisation Primary Contact Suffix
LogicalColumn.Description: Organisation Primary Contact Suffix: The suffix of the Supporter who is marked as a Primary Contact for an Organisation.

LogicalColumn.name: Organisation Primary Contact Title
LogicalColumn.Description: Title: The Title of the Supporter who is marked as a Primary Contact for an Organisation (e.g. 'Mr', 'Mrs' etc.)

LogicalColumn.name: Supporter Mosaic Type
LogicalColumn.Description: Refers to the different types in which UK population has been categorised by Mosaic UK, which is Experian's people classification system

LogicalColumn.name: Supporter Mosaic Group
LogicalColumn.Description: Refers to the main socio-economic groups in which UK population has been categorised by Mosaic UK, which is Experian's people classification system

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: EVALUATE('FLOOR(MONTHS_BETWEEN(%1, %2)/12)', CASE WHEN "%1" IS NULL THEN CURRENT_DATE ELSE "%1" END , "%2")

Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" < 1 THEN 'Less than 1 year' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" >= 1 AND "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" < 2 THEN '1 - 2 years' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" >= 2 AND "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" < 3 THEN '2 - 3 years' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" >= 3 AND "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" < 5 THEN '3 - 5 years' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" >= 5 AND "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" < 10 THEN '5 - 10 years' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" >= 10 AND "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" < 15 THEN '10 - 15 years' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" >= 15 AND "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" < 20 THEN '15 - 20 years' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" >= 20 AND "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" < 25 THEN '20 - 25 years' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" >= 25 AND "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" < 30 THEN '25 - 30 years' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" >= 30 AND "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" < 35 THEN '30 - 35 years' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" >= 35 AND "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" < 40 THEN '35 - 40 years' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" >= 40 AND "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" < 45 THEN '40 - Owning Party"."Years of Service" >= 60 AND "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" < 80 THEN '60 - 80 years' WHEN "Core 2"."Dim - Owning Party"."Years of Service" >= 80 THEN '80+ years' END
